==English==
===Noun===
'''fig''' (''plural'' '''figs''')

#A tree or [[shrub]] of the genus ''Ficus'' that is native mainly to the [[tropics]] and produces a fruit of the same name.
#The fruit of the fig, [[pear]]-shaped and containing many small seeds.

